title: Episode 10 - No New Friends???
description:
"I'm meeting new people and nervous about really getting close with them."
No New Friends???
Ehlie Luna
Ehlie is one of the most naturally talented and creative people I know. She is a true renaissance woman and one of my closest friends. You'll hear us explore how to enjoy all of your interests and lean into your strengths.
Show Topics:
Growing your inner circle
Aligning yourself with people who believe what you believe
How to energetically align yourself with you
Leaning into possibilities by exploring your creative interests
Why good friends are SO important in this life
--
Born and raised in Brooklyn, NY, Ehlie Luna is a Haitian-American artist specializing in makeup and content creation. She aims to make the beauty space more accessible thru education and entertainment, sharing over a decade of professional experience. Ehlie also aims to help creators in this space find their unique voice.
Follow Ehlie on Instagram @ehlieluna.
--
This is Delina's village and you're about to be a part of it. Welcome to It Takes A Village, The True Story of A Beautypreneur.
